summary: Phatt - By Matt Furie - Phatt Pepe is the plus sized version of Pepe the frog, and is part of the Zogz Family created by Matt Furie. Phatt Pepe is known to spread happiness and positivity to internet users of all sizes. Phatt Coin shares a form of internet humour that can take on many different shapes and styles. Phatt Coin is a fully decentralized, community-powered meme token built on the Ethereum Network as an ERC-20 Token.
